<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Returns & Refunds</h1>
        <p class="lead text-body-secondary">We want you to love your purchase. If you don't, we're here to help.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-header d-flex align-items-center bg-transparent border-0 pt-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-patch-check-fill fs-4 me-2 text-dark"></i>
                    <h4 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Our Return Policy</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-text text-body-secondary">To be eligible for a return, your item must meet the following criteria. Please note that sale items and gift cards are non-returnable.</p>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mt-3">
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center ps-0">
                            <i class="bi bi-calendar3 text-dark me-3 fs-5"></i>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="mb-0">30-Day Window</h6>
                                <small class="text-body-secondary">You have 30 days after receiving your item to request a return.</small>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center ps-0">
                            <i class="bi bi-box-seam text-dark me-3 fs-5"></i>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="mb-0">Original Condition</h6>
                                <small class="text-body-secondary">Items must be unworn or unused, with tags, and in their original packaging.</small>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                         <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center ps-0">
                            <i class="bi bi-receipt text-dark me-3 fs-5"></i>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="mb-0">Proof of Purchase</h6>
                                <small class="text-body-secondary">You’ll need the receipt or proof of purchase to complete your return.</small>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                 <div class="card-header d-flex align-items-center bg-transparent border-0 pt-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-left fs-4 me-2 text-dark"></i>
                    <h4 class="mb-0 fw-bold">How to Start a Return</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <ol class="list-unstyled d-flex flex-column gap-4">
                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                            <div class="fs-4 text-dark"><i class="bi bi-1-circle-fill"></i></div>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="fw-semibold">Initiate Request</h6>
                                <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0">Go to our <a href="/support/contact">Contact Us</a> page, select "Return Request" as the subject, and provide your order details in the message.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                            <div class="fs-4 text-dark"><i class="bi bi-2-circle-fill"></i></div>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="fw-semibold">Receive Label & Instructions</h6>
                                <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0">Our team will review your request. If approved, you'll get a prepaid shipping label and instructions via email in 1-2 business days.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                            <div class="fs-4 text-dark"><i class="bi bi-3-circle-fill"></i></div>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="fw-semibold">Package & Ship</h6>
                                <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0">Securely pack the items in the original packaging, attach the return label, and drop it off at any local courier partner.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header d-flex align-items-center bg-transparent border-0 pt-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-wallet2 fs-4 me-2 text-dark"></i>
                    <h4 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Refunds</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0">We will notify you once we’ve received and inspected your return. If approved, you’ll be automatically refunded on your original payment method within 10 business days. Please remember it can take some time for your bank or credit card company to process and post the refund, too.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="support-sidebar-card">
                <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">Quick Links</h5>
                <ul class="list-unstyled d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                    <li>
                        <a href="/support/order-status" class="text-dark fw-medium d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-box-seam"></i>
                            <span>Track Your Order</span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/support/shipping" class="text-dark fw-medium d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-truck"></i>
                            <span>Shipping Policy</span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/support/contact" class="text-dark fw-medium d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-headset"></i>
                            <span>Contact Support</span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>